{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b1f45a64-5c6d-4f85-985e-refund-cancel-checklist",
    "name": "CloseExp - Refund & Cancel Checklist",
    "description": "Collection test theo checklist BE API + email job + FE cho luong paid/cancel/refund.\n\nHuong dan nhanh:\n1) Dang nhap user chu don -> luu userToken + orderId\n2) Paid order -> test cancel trong han / qua han\n3) Kiem tra refund theo role user khac nhau\n4) Kiem tra transition approved/rejected/completed bang token Admin/MarketingStaff\n5) Xac minh email theo log/mailbox theo folder manual checklist\n\nLuu y:\n- Khong hardcode token, su dung bien collection\n- Cac case qua han can order da vuot cancelDeadline\n- Case inventory/hoan kho can doi chieu DB neu can",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5014/api" },
    { "key": "userToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "otherUserToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "marketingToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refundId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0 - Setup Tokens",
      "description": "Gan token thu cong hoac login bang request phu hop cua he thong.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Orders/{orderId} (seed check)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{userToken}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/Orders/{{orderId}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1 - Order Paid -> Cancel Window",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "PUT Orders/{id}/paid",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Paid success', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 204]);",
                  "});",
                  "try {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j && j.data && j.data.cancelDeadline) {",
                  "    console.log('cancelDeadline:', j.data.cancelDeadline);",
                  "  }",
                  "} catch (e) {",
                  "  // No JSON body is acceptable for 204",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{userToken}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/Orders/{{orderId}}/paid",
            "description": "Ky vong: he thong set CancelDeadline theo config ORDER_CANCEL_WINDOW_MINUTES_AFTER_PAID."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Orders/{id}/canceled (trong han)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Cancel in window success', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 204]);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{userToken}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Test huy trong han (Postman)\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/Orders/{{orderId}}/canceled",
            "description": "Ky vong: Order -> Canceled; hoan kho thanh cong. Body bat buoc: { reason }. Khong tu tao Refund — tao refund bang API Refunds neu can."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Orders/{id}/canceled (qua han)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Cancel after deadline rejected', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(400);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{userToken}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Test huy sau han (Postman)\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/Orders/{{orderId}}/canceled",
            "description": "Dung order da qua cancelDeadline. Ky vong 400 voi message qua thoi gian cho phep huy. Van can reason trong body."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2 - Refund Visibility & Permissions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Refunds/my?orderId={orderId} (owner token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Owner can see own refund list', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "});",
                  "try {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  const first = j?.data?.items?.[0] || j?.data?.[0];",
                  "  if (first?.id || first?.refundId) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refundId', first.id || first.refundId);",
                  "  }",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{userToken}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/Refunds/my?orderId={{orderId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Refunds/my?orderId={orderId} (other user token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Other user cannot see owner refund data', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "});",
                  "try {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  const items = j?.data?.items || j?.data || [];",
                  "  pm.expect(items.length).to.equal(0);",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{otherUserToken}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/Refunds/my?orderId={{orderId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Refunds (admin token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Admin can access all refunds', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
